Search tool&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>linux</category><category>setup</category><category>ubuntu</category><guid>http://www.SoftDevTrain.com/posts/setting-up-new-ubuntu-workstation.html</guid><pubDate>Tue, 20 Mar 2018 16:32:25 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>